{"tid":731631,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啲女人真係冇性架！！！","createTime":"2018-07-06T10:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T17:20:53.000Z","uid":36868,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a2fa96c35903e60154703f5899db4b8ffcc382b5","tid":731631,"uid":36868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"話說小弟番個份工經常會比人問點稱呼，<br />\n久而久之一比人問都會好順口咁答「我姓鄧」咁。<br />\n工作關係鄧生鄧生咁叫其實係冇問題！！！<br />\n<br />\n前排女友就話冇帶過我去見佢啲姊妹，今日帶我去同佢地食餐飯咁話。我都心知不妙，今晚一定好撚難過。<br />\n<br />\n一見到就當然第一句就比人問「xx男友，我地叫你咩好」<br />\n我口快快工作mode講咗句「係 我姓鄧」<br />\n屌你老母即刻全場靜撚哂再爆笑<br />\n連續3條女笑住咁講「我姓李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」「我都係姓李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」「咦，我都係姓李wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」再自己係度笑笑笑<br />\n<br />\n屌哂佢地老母我依家就係廁所出post批鬥佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d54b4b3b6c164e889eff90a3faa07ccdcc0f706","tid":731631,"uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"樓主好威 上post隔空屌佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a4fa714d531cf159cbb7e59232870d4f201628","tid":731631,"uid":20241,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"屌你去廁所去咁耐我地以為你便秘呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小姐上"},{"pid":"3996418434ce05bcb420cedd2cf0786a7bcd6943","tid":731631,"uid":189386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"幾好丫，起碼你有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6826aa6ca3b54ec21019ba269e0c45ae5d4cdea7","tid":731631,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"同佢地性愛"},{"pid":"4df89e3c164ed8c6707c5a281613bdfad310f404","tid":731631,"